description: Strengthening national capacities for youth professional and technical training   at Industrial Training National Center. (Centre National de Formation Industriel - CENFI)

subproject.corporate outcome: Capacities of national and local institutions enhanced to scale up proven MDG acceleration interventions and to plan, monitor, report and evaluate the MDG progress in the context of related national development priorities
subproject.description: The capacities of trainers and of CENFI are enhanced to diversify and improve the quality of technical and professional training; the openness of the CENFI to the world is promoted trough the NTCI and other educational materials (books, reviews, etc.) and One hundred Youth benefit from training.
subproject.title: Strength capacity of CENFI
